 @* ----- Card Layout ----- *@
                            <div class="pd-product-card__badge"> @* Starts a layout container for this section. *@
                                <!-- Stock status badge --> @* Keeps an existing comment in the Razor file. *@
 @* ----- Conditional Rendering ----- *@
