                                        <!-- Low-stock badge --> @* Keeps an existing comment in the Razor file. *@
                                        <i data-lucide="zap" class="pw-icon-sm"></i> <!-- Zap icon --> @* Renders part of the producers page markup. *@
                                        Low Stock @* Renders part of the producers page markup. *@
                                    </span> @* Closes the matching HTML element. *@
                                }
 @* ----- Conditional Rendering ----- *@
                                else // Plenty in stock @* Renders the fallback branch for the previous condition. *@
